OL,3,CCumbrian MP welcomes new road safety
OL,4,Cmeasures
OL,6,FA Cumbrian MP says a junction on the
OL,7,FM6 is likely to become safer after the
OL,8,Finstallation of new road improvements.
OL,10,FRoadworks have taken place to change
OL,11,Fdrivers behaviour on the A684 at
OL,12,FJunction 37 of the M6 - the aim is to
OL,13,Freduce the number of incidents on the
OL,14,Fmotorway.
OL,16,FTim Farron, Liberal Democrats MP for
OL,17,FWestmorland and Lonsdale, says it is
OL,18,F"completely unacceptable" that three
OL,19,Fpeople have lost their lives since
OL,20,FJuly 2024.
