OL,3,CCumbrian MP welcomes new road safety
OL,4,Cmeasures
OL,6,FHe said: "Very often it's like a
OL,7,Fshooting alley when people are bombing
OL,8,Fin east to west, and then people
OL,9,Fcoming off the motorway sometimes not
OL,10,Flooking. The consequences are lots of
OL,11,Faccidents and several tragedies.
OL,13,F"Spending public money on trying to
OL,14,Fmake sure that doesn't happen in the
OL,15,Ffuture is the right thing to do. We
OL,16,Foften complain when the powers that be
OL,17,Fdon't do what we ask them to do, but
OL,18,Fin this particular case we fought hard
OL,19,Fin the last few of months for upgrades.
