OL,3,CCumbrian MP welcomes new road safety
OL,4,Cmeasures
OL,6,F"They have given us that and thats
OL,7,Fsomething to be grateful for. What
OL,8,Fmyself and the local community have
OL,9,Fbeen campaigning for, National
OL,10,FHighways and the local council have
OL,11,Fagreed to do."
OL,13,FWestmorland and Furness Council are
OL,14,Fintroducing 500m of road markings, an
OL,15,Fincrease of driver visibility at night
OL,16,Ftime and reduced speeds.
OL,18,FThe safety improvements led to periods
OL,19,Fof a full road closure from 11
OL,20,FNovember - 14 November 2024.
