OL,3,CCumbrian MP welcomes new road safety
OL,4,Cmeasures
OL,6,FThe Council in partnership with
OL,7,FCumbria Constabulary and National
OL,8,FHighways, decided to implement the
OL,9,Fmeasures following a series of serious
OL,10,Fcollisions on the slip road of the M6.
OL,12,FThe roadworks include double white
OL,13,Fcentre lines, road studs, yellow
OL,14,F'rumble strips', red high friction
OL,15,Fbanding and signage across 500m of
OL,16,Froad.
OL,18,FNational Highways are expected to make
OL,19,Ffurther safety improvements to the M6
OL,20,Fslipway in the near future.
