OL,3,CCumbrian MP welcomes new road safety
OL,4,Cmeasures
OL,6,F"Our lining improvements on the A684
OL,7,Fmark the start of a multi-agency
OL,8,Fprogramme to reduce the risk of
OL,9,Ffurther incidents here.
OL,11,F"Our works are designed to calm
OL,12,Ftraffic, discourage overtaking, and
OL,13,Fensure that drivers have a clearer
OL,14,Fview of the road ahead, especially at
OL,15,Fnight."
